Queries

allActivities

Response

Returns [Activity]

Example

Query
query allActivities {
  allActivities {
    _id
    code
    description
    _createdAt
    _updatedAt
  }
}
Response
{
  "data": {
    "allActivities": [
      {
        "_id": "xyz789",
        "code": "abc123",
        "description": "abc123",
        "_createdAt": "abc123",
        "_updatedAt": "abc123"
      }
    ]
  }
}

allBasicCocoaStatisticCultivatedAreas

Response

Returns [BasicCocoaStatisticCultivatedArea]

Example

Query
query allBasicCocoaStatisticCultivatedAreas {
  allBasicCocoaStatisticCultivatedAreas {
    _id
    year
    LocalRegion {
      _id
      code
      description
      _createdAt
      _updatedAt
    }
    LocalState {
      _id
      code
      description
      LocalRegion {
        ...LocalRegionFragment
      }
      _createdAt
      _updatedAt
    }
    InfoStatus {
      _id
      code
      description
      _createdAt
      _updatedAt
    }
    estateNo
    estateArea
    smallhNo
    smallhArea
    maturedArea
    _createdAt
    _updatedAt
  }
}

  "data": {
    "allBasicCocoaStatisticCultivatedAreas": [
      {
        "_id": "xyz789",
        "year": 123,
        "LocalRegion": LocalRegion,
        "LocalState": LocalState,
        "InfoStatus": InfoStatus,
        "estateNo": 987.65,
        "estateArea": 987.65,
        "smallhNo": 123.45,
        "smallhArea": 987.65,
        "maturedArea": 123.45,
        "_createdAt": "abc123",
        "_updatedAt": "xyz789"
      }
    ]
  }
}

    importedPurchase

    grindingsCapacity

      cocoaButter
      cocoaLiquorMass
      cocoaPowder
      cocoaCake
    }

      cocoaPowder
      cocoaCake
    }

    _createdAt
    _updatedAt
  }
}

        "_id": "xyz789",

        "importedPurchase": 987.65,
        "grindingsTotal": 123.45,
